CRITICAL LICENSE COMPLIANCE INFORMATION:
---------------------------------------

Due to the high degree of licensing heterogeneity, this repository contains components 
under incompatible licenses (particularly GPL-2.0, GPL-3.0, and non-commercial licenses).

